name: DEN_barbuccisketch
description:
Made as a counter part to my Barbucci art style and works well along side of this to make sketches and drawn images of the style.

an interesting side affect has been the addition of intricate details to other works, so i would love to see the results of work from this. it is aimed at drawings and black and white, but it is making some interesting stuff from other checkpoints.
